Package ohos.data.resultset

Class TableResultSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.resultset.AbsResultSet
      • ohos.data.resultset.TableResultSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ResultSet

    public class TableResultSet
extends AbsResultSet
    Represents a table result set that can be expanded dynamically.

    The result set is stored in a two-dimensional Object array, and the addRow() method is used to add rows to the result set.

    Since:
    2
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_APPDATAMGR
